麦当娜和死亡金属之鹰向巴黎恐怖袭击周年致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-and-eagles-of-death-metal-pay-tribute-on-anniversary-of-paris-terror-attacks-3539005?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=麦当娜和死亡之鹰向巴黎恐怖袭击周年致敬Anagricel DuranTue, 14 Nov 2023 20:15:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3539005 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="麦当娜和死亡金属之鹰。图片来源：Kevin Mazur 和 Didier Messens" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>八年前的袭击造成80多人死亡</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-and-eagles-of-death-metal-pay-tribute-on-anniversary-of-paris-terror-attacks-3539005">麦当娜和死亡金属之鹰致敬巴黎恐怖袭击周年纪念日的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="麦当娜和死亡金属之鹰。图片来源：Kevin Mazur 和 Didier Messens" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Madonna-and-Eagles-of-Death-Metal-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/madonna">麦当娜</a>和<a href="/artists/eagles-of-death-metal">死亡金属之鹰</a>都庆祝了 2015 年巴黎恐怖袭击周年纪念日。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/madonna-celebration-tour-review-setlist-3515338">麦当娜在伦敦现场演出：流行天后努力应对她的遗产</a></strong></li></ul><p>周一（11 月 13 日）在巴黎举行的“Celebration”世界巡演期间，这位流行偶像花了一些时间回顾八年前袭击这座城市的袭击事件。</p><p> 2015 年 11 月 13 日，Eagles Of Death Metal 在巴黎巴塔克兰音乐厅举行的演出中，89 人被恐怖分子杀害，这是法国首都周围一系列袭击的一部分。</p><p> 2015 年，在她的“Rebel Hearts”巡演期间，这位歌手和她的儿子大卫·班达 (David Banda) 参观了巴塔克兰剧院附近的共和广场，向袭击受害者表示哀悼。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">麦当娜昨晚在 Accor Arena 演讲的另一段摘录 – IG 上的较长剪辑。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/MadonnaCelebrationTour?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#MadonnaCelebrationTour</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Paris?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#巴黎</a><a href="https://t.co/HI4uRVJQtU">pic.twitter.com/HI4uRVJQtU</a></p><p> - MadonnaTribe (@madonnatribe) <a href="https://twitter.com/madonnatribe/status/1724314146664071621?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 11 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “这是一个悲惨的事件，我记得上次我来这里参加“叛逆之心”巡演时，我在共和国广场与大卫一起唱歌——我无法承认这一悲剧。但这样的悲剧却不断发生，永远不会结束。有时你可以问自己，它什么时候结束，以及作为人类我们能做些什么来改变它？”麦当娜在周一晚上的演出中说道（据<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/166133/Madonna-honours-anniversary-of-Paris-terror-attacks" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《音乐新闻</em></a>》）。</p><p>死亡金属之鹰还通过在他们的官方 Facebook 页面上分享了埃德·哈考特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-of-death-metal-25-1201265">(Ed Harcourt) 翻唱的</a>法国国旗片段来纪念袭击事件周年。</p><p>去年，乐队主唱杰西·休斯 (Jesse Hughes) 和吉他手伊登·加林多 (Eden Galindo) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-of-death-metal-testify-over-2015-bataclan-terrorist-attack-the-perpetrators-tried-to-leave-a-legacy-of-terror-3228008">于 5 月 17 日出庭，在巴黎正在进行的围绕袭击事件的民事审判中作证</a>。</p><p>两位乐队成员都描述了这次袭击如何永久地影响了他们作为幸存者。据<em><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/may/17/eagles-of-death-metal-tell-paris-terror-trial-how-band-ran-for-their-lives" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《卫报》</a></em>报道，当乐队演奏歌曲《Kiss The Devil》时，休斯立即知道场地受到攻击。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzlNNAXrLvg/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,3